Class Borrowing

java.lang.Object
entity.Borrowing
@Entity public class Borrowing extends Object
Represents a record that a user borrowed a particular copy of a book. Each borrowing links a user to a copy of a book with associated dates for borrowing and returning. The user who borrowed the book. Many borrowings can reference one user. The date when the book was returned. Can be null if the book has not been returned yet.
